# {{lb|en|often|pejorative}} A [[pedantic]] senior person of influence in [[academia]] or [[literary]] circles.
#: {{rfquote-sense|lang=en}}
# {{lb|en|ornithology}} {{ellipsis|mandarin duck|lang=en}}.
# {{lb|en|informal|British}} A senior [[civil servant]].

